        <briefdescription>
<para>Set input report polling period. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Similar to devicetree property in-polling-period-us, but it allows setting different polling periods at runtime.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="attention"><para>Available only when the following Kconfig option is enabled: <computeroutput>CONFIG_USBD_HID_SET_POLLING_PERIOD</computeroutput>.</para>
</simplesect>
